
graph TD
    User((User)) -->|HTTPS| Frontend[React Client]
    
    subgraph "Core System"
        Frontend -->|REST / Socket| API[NestJS API Gateway]
        API -->|Auth/Data| DB[(PostgreSQL)]
        API -->|Uploads| MinIO[MinIO Storage]
        API -->|Real-time| Redis[(Redis)]
    end
    
    subgraph "AI System (Python)"
        API -->|HTTP Request| Vision[FastAPI Service]
        Vision -->|Load Model| CLIP[CLIP Model]
        Vision -->|Vector Search| Milvus[(Milvus Vector DB)]
    end